## Tech stack (short)

- **Beats:** Supabase `beats` — `api/beats.js`, `pending-beats.js`, `manage-beat.js`, `submit-beat.js`; Review in Supabase Table Editor (`beat_status` enum)
- Auth/profiles: Supabase (RLS on). Favorites: `api/crate.js` + service role
